INSERT INTO prompt_version (
                prompt_id,
                version_number,
                system_diff,
                user_diff,
                system,
                user,
                model_id,
                max_tokens,
                temperature,
                json_mode,
                json_schema,
                prompt_type,
                is_chat
            )
            VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
